  31:movi_comm.c   ****  * Big-endian read helpers.
ARM GAS  C:\Users\JENNEW~1\AppData\Local\Temp\ccCcCinD.s 			page 2


  32:movi_comm.c   ****  * GPS (attr 4) and sysstat (attr 1) payload bytes are big-endian and have
  33:movi_comm.c   ****  * NO sub-index byte — data starts at offset 0.  Confirmed by cross-checking
  34:movi_comm.c   ****  * against iOS app ground-truth values (lon/lat/batt_v/temp/pressure).
  35:movi_comm.c   ****  * Attr 22 (attitude) is little-endian with a 0x00 sub-index at offset 0.
  36:movi_comm.c   ****  * ----------------------------------------------------------------------- */
